text: Robert Löfman (22 July 1875 - 8 January 1940) was a Swedish sports shooter. He competed in three events at the 1912 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1875 births Category:1940 deaths Category:Swedish male sport shooters Category:Olympic shooters of Sweden Category:Shooters at the 1912 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Stockholm
